<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>WHY NOT TO-NIGHT?</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Na phat hih mawkin mangbei ki'n,
 Pathien Thu kizak mawh sak ki'n;
 Migilo, na lungkhauh sak ki'n,
 Tu'n hun awi ngal in.

[V2]
 Bang di'n awi nuom lo?
 Bang na uoi-ai em?
 Awiin, dam na'n,
 Bang di'n awi nuomlo?

[V3]
 2. Zing khawvak le na mulo thei,
 Zan khat mitsin tuok thei na hi;
 Suohpih, sanggam, nu-le-pate,
 Tu'n hun awi ngal un.

[V4]
 3. Ama'n A hun lainat ngal in,
 Nang Amah bengkhawn loh guo maw;
 Na dahna cheng hun nultha'n la,
 Tu'n hun awi ngal un.

[V5]
 4. Pathien hehpihna'n A dim hi,
 Kuole Amah kawma nuom chuh;
 A tawp chanin A hukdam thei,
 Tu'n hun awi tei un.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>243</hymn_number>
</song>